    "title": "Front Office Manager - Beyond Wildlife India Asia Pacific Associates - Attractive Package",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Front Office Manager with drive and ambition, Beyond Wildlife India Asia Pacific Associates in Varanasi is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Beyond Wildlife India Asia Pacific Associates:\nBeyond Wildlife India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Beyond Wildlife India Asia Pacific Associates!",
